title: Watch moment police find crying child underneath rubble of a home blast
description: Bodycam footage shows police rescuing an Indiana family from debris after an explosion in their home.

title: 'Deepfake' Queen delivers alternative Christmas speech
description: A fake Queen Elizabeth danced across TV screens on Christmas as part of a "deepfake" speech aired by a British broadcaster.

title: Social media video shows scene of explosion in Nashville
description: Footage shows damage at the scene of an explosion in Nashville on Christmas Day. Police believe the explosion was intentional.

title: Footage shows Russian police raiding home of activist
description: Police raided the home of Russian opposition activist Lyubov Sobol and took her in for questioning, according to a series of tweets from opposition leader Alexey Navalny and his team. CNN's Fred Pleitgen reports.

title: Behind the scenes of a famous James Bond shoot
description: A supervillain, an assassin, a mountain car chase and an Aston Martin equipped with gadgetry -- the Alpine scenes in 1964's "Goldfinger" set a new benchmark for the archetypal James Bond sequence. And as well as being, arguably, the most iconic six minutes and 37 seconds in the franchise's history, it is also one of the best documented.

title: Boeing 737: How world's most successful airplane became its most troubled
description: Over the course of its long history, the Boeing 737 has acquired more nicknames than any other commercial aircraft.

title: The major events that changed the world in 2020
description: 2020 has been an unforgettable year. We've witnessed world-changing, paradigm-shifting events, all under the cloud of the Covid-19 pandemic.  CNN's Clarissa Ward looks back at the major international events of the year.

title: The week in 21 photos
description: Take a look at 21 photos of the week from December 17 through December 25.
